'''赫拉神廟'''（Temple of Hera）是一座[[古希臘神廟|古希臘神廟]]遺跡，位於[[奧林匹亞|奧林匹亞]]。這座神廟奉獻給希臘神話中的女神[[赫拉|赫拉]]<ref name=Darling>{{cite book|last1=Darling|first1=Janina K.|authorlink1=Temple of Hera, Olympia|title=Architecture of Greece|date=2004|publisher=Greenwood Publishing Group|pages=195–197|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=4F-v35--l_gC&pg=PA195|accessdate=19 November 2015|isbn=9780313321528}}</ref>，是奧林匹亞最古老的神廟。赫拉神廟最初同時獻給赫拉和宙斯，但後來宙斯有了單獨的神廟<ref>{{cite book |last1=Doniger |first1=Wendy |title=Britannica Encyclopedia of World Religions |date=March 1, 2006 |publisher=Encyclopaedia Britannica, Inc.}}</ref>。奧林匹克聖火在這座神廟點燃<ref>{{cite web |title=Ancient Olympia |url=https://www.greeka.com/peloponnese/olympia/sightseeing/temple-hera/ |website=Greeka |accessdate=18 January 2020 |archive-date=2021-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210119135643/https://www.greeka.com/peloponnese/olympia/sightseeing/temple-hera/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{citation|url=http://www.olympic.org/documents/reports/en/en_report_655.pdf|title=The Olympic Flame and the Torch Relay|page=4|accessdate=19 November 2015|archive-date=2016-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160328062450/http://www.olympic.org/Documents/Reports/EN/en_report_655.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。神廟約修建於西元前530年，但在西元前4世紀初期因地震被毀。
